{
  "texts": [
    "Should a certain threshold have been met before a person is acknowledged?",
    "Are the names in alphabetical order, ranked, and/or even connected to the individual output?",
    "The form should also provide information on how personal information is stored and kept safe.",
    "However, one can imagine that, especially for larger projects which have already started, asking every individual member of the crowd for their consent can result in an administrative nightmare.",
    "There is an 'opt-out' method for these cases to deal with the GDPR."
  ]
}